{"tid":2076012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［連登仔點睇？］吳傲雪冀連登仔勿二次傷害","createTime":"2020-06-23T08:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T08:40:58.000Z","uid":58335,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"978d553216511c041494be9784af7f47b13b426d","tid":2076012,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:21:26.000Z","msg":"港版有村架純呼籲大家勿二次傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾公開指控受到警方性暴力的吳傲雪，今年2月創辦組織Stand with you，協助警暴受害人，包括提供法律、心理、經濟支援等，K同學正是求助人之一，全部求助人都曾遭受警方性暴力，當中超過一半人被控襲警，「好懷疑警方係報復」。<br />\n<br />\n「我哋行出嚟唔係選美」<br />\n<br />\n吳傲雪稱，早在去年10月已收集受害個案，至今共接獲近50宗個案，全部涉及警方性罪行，包括言語及肢體上的性侵犯，暫未有涉強姦個案。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">吳呼籲社會大眾、尤其連登討論區的網民對性暴力受害人「高抬貴手」，切勿對受害人評頭品足，而是多些關愛，「我哋行出嚟唔係選美，我哋行出嚟係希望鼓勵同路人有勇氣一齊行落去，同行。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/TBOFN7URRNKUQHWMYYKZ2S5YSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FTBOFN7URRNKUQHWMYYKZ2S5YSQ%2F&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=223690a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FTBOFN7URRNKUQHWMYYKZ2S5YSQ%2F&h=52e68cdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/TBOFN7URRNKUQHWMYYKZ2S5YSQ/</a>"},{"pid":"34feb98711797e3fb1b63ab727757a8fa2a68961","tid":2076012,"uid":106336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:22:15.000Z","msg":"其實佢冇錯架喎"},{"pid":"fe9cb77f7eed8e3c454de7bff215dbe19ae587a5","tid":2076012,"uid":173179,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"34feb98711797e3fb1b63ab727757a8fa2a68961","tid":2076012,"uid":106336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:22:15.000Z","msg":"其實佢冇錯架喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:26:24.000Z","msg":"的確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b27b6